Class GetCollectionNoteParameter

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.communote.plugins.api.rest.resource.note.GetCollectionNoteParameter

  • public class GetCollectionNoteParameter
extends Object
    This class it the parameter class for the Note resource. It covers all the parameter and attributes of the HTTP GETCOLLECTION method.
